  <brief_title>Effects of a Dietary Fibre Supplementation of a Low Calorie Diet on Appetite and Body Weight</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo Controlled Trial Evaluating the Effects of a High Viscosity Dietary Fibre (PGX) Supplementation of a Low Calorie Diet on Appetite and Body Weight, in Overweight and Moderately Obese Females</official_title>
